{"tid":1702213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學界和你罷] 大學生不如同大人一齊罷? 禮拜一堵塞大學主要教學大樓好唔好?","createTime":"2019-11-09T14:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T16:18:19.000Z","uid":199727,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca406069297aedc3f428df0f6a8b72b6b2d9729","tid":1702213,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"大人話罷工會被上司清算，唔緊要，我地令到你返唔到工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大學生話要Take attendence唔緊要 ，我地就令到你有excuse同professor解釋上唔到堂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大人都肯企出黎，唔通大學生仲要活喺平行時空? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地肯放棄生計為我地罷工，唔通你地甘心背棄佢地而走去上堂但實際可能只係玩手機同訓教? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我希望大專生一齊喺禮拜一既朝早八點配合黎明行動，一齊堵塞大學入面既主要教學大樓，等同學同教師進入唔到裡面上課。但係我希望大家珍惜大學既資源，唔好刻意破壞，只用合理既物資去堵塞入口。(例如借美心Canteen啲野去塞)  大學生團結一次啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a6e170261c76043f1df18df6f2a21192a19416","tid":1702213,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/win